TextField for entering email address

Placeholder text

Real-time validation

Module 2: Email Validation Module

Regex pattern used:

^[A-Za-z0-9+_.-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+$

Module 3: GUI Display Module

Modern UI

Color feedback

Status text like ‚ÄúValid Email ‚úì‚Äù or ‚ÄúInvalid Email ‚úó‚Äù

Module 4: Controller Module

Event handling

Connects user UI to validation logic

Updates GUI status

12. ALGORITHMS USED
A. Email Validation Algorithm
1. Read input email
2. Match with regex pattern
3. If matches ‚Üí display "Valid Email"
4. Else ‚Üí display "Invalid Email"

B. Regex Pattern Matching

Checks for:

‚úî local-part
‚úî @ symbol
‚úî domain name
‚úî domain extension (.com, .org, etc.)

