15. CONCLUSION

Email Format Validator provides a high-quality GUI-based system for validating email formats quickly and accurately.
Its use of JavaFX, regex, MVC, and user-friendly interface makes it suitable for real applications as well as academic submissions.
The application is reliable, extensible, and demonstrates excellent software engineering principles.
